Package smartgov.urban.osm.environment.graph

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    OsmArc
    Class used to represent arcs between OsmNodes.
    OsmNode
    Class used to represents OSM nodes, i.e. crossroads and line breaks.
    OsmWay
    Minimal representation of an osm way.
    Road
    A Road is a particular OsmWay where agents can move.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    OsmArc.RoadDirection
    Used to represent the direction represented by an arc in the osm road.
    Road.OneWay
    Describe the oneway status of a road, according to the official OSM tag documentation.
